f(x) = \sqrt{r^2 - x^2}
dA = 2 \pi f(x) dx
A = \int_{-r}^r dA
 = 2 \pi \int_{-r}^r f(x) dx
 = 2 \pi (\frac{\pi r^2}{2})
 = \pi^2 r^2
