n\to\infty
\begin{align*} \text{Error per interval} &= \text{Actual area} - \text{Computed area}\\ &= \left(\frac{x}{n} + \frac{1}{2n^2}\right) - \frac{x}{n} = \frac{1}{2n^2}. \end{align*}
